author: Brittany Vincent
title: Finally, The Lowrider of Your Dreams Is Waiting For You in GTA Online
text:
Ever wanted to drive around a lowrider in Grand Theft Auto V's stunning fictional vision of sunny California? For the longest time, players weren't able to do so. That's all changed with the latest update coming to the game's online component, GTA Online .
Beginning on October 20th, players will be able to cruise around in eye-popping lowriders. But the cars aren't the main attraction. Rockstar has also stressed that there's an additional story element to the new rides. Grand Theft Auto protagonist Lamar is going to challenge the gangs of Los Santos in the lowrider scene.
It's all starting next week. Better start curating the proper lowrider soundtrack in-game to get ready.
